Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:26.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ame agari no sora wo aogu tabi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:31.42,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I look up to \Nthe sky after the rain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.44,0:00:31.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nakimushi datta koro no boku wo omou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.44,0:00:37.13,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I think back to when I was a crybaby
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:37.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dareka no senaka wo gamushara ni oikaketa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:44.89,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chasing somebody's back blindly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.91,0:00:44.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"tsuyoku naritai" tte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.91,0:00:47.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking "I want to be stronger"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.75,0:00:47.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ima wa kaze ni kieta "arigatou"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.75,0:00:53.19,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The word "thank you" has \Nfaded into the wind now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.21,0:00:53.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku wa tsuyoku nareteiru no kana?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.21,0:00:58.36,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I getting stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.38,0:00:58.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kotae wa mada desou ni nai kara sa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.38,0:01:04.04,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the answer yet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.06,0:01:04.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yappari mada aruiteiku yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.06,0:01:09.62,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll keep walking ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:09.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:11.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.85,0:01:11.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.85,0:01:15.17,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.19,0:01:15.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.19,0:01:20.42,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.44,0:01:20.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.44,0:01:25.98,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.00,0:01:25.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.00,0:01:31.40,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.42,0:01:31.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku no naka ni nagareru koe wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.42,0:01:36.82,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The voice inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.84,0:01:36.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,zutto zutto boku wo sasaeteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.84,0:01:42.17,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,keeps sustaining me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.19,0:01:42.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,itazura na ame ga jama suru kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.19,0:01:47.39,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked rain will get in my way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.41,0:01:47.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nigedasanai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.41,0:01:52.39,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't walk away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.41,0:01:52.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.41,0:01:55.38,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.40,0:01:55.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.40,0:01:57.67,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.69,0:01:57.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.69,0:02:00.96,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.98,0:02:00.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.98,0:02:06.18,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:06.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:11.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:11.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:17.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:17.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinjita sono saki e to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:25.48,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,To the future I believe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.86,0:02:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.94,0:02:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.94,0:02:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.78,0:02:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, \Na boy whose body turned to rubber
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.69,0:02:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.61,0:02:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become\N the next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.52,0:03:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and\N less able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.42,0:03:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.82,0:03:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.11,0:03:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.26,0:03:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.75,0:03:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Separated from the rest of the Straw Hats,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy made it to Marineford to rescue \Nhis brother, Ace who will be executed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.05,0:03:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and the Whitebeards\N are trying to get to the scaffold
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the Navy stands in their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.08,0:03:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle is heating up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then suddenly, a group of \Nthe Navy's human weapons -
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.06,0:03:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Pacifistas appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the bay head! There's something!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.55,0:03:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the human weapon of \Nthe Government that I heard of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.45,0:04:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Extermination Strategy in Action! \NThe Power of the Pacifistas!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.54,0:04:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Warlord--Bartholomew Kuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come there're so many Kumas?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.32,0:04:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the ones who ran wild \Nhere on the Sabaody a while ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There're a number of Bartholomew Kumas!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now they've got way more of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Head Office! Head Office!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.21,0:05:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have big news!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.21,0:05:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the real one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.56,0:05:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard about it from time to time
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.94,0:05:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that Dr. Vegapunk was trying \Nto build a human weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and was repeatedly sending \Nprototypes to various places.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.35,0:05:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they're the human weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do they all look like Kuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle! Didn't everything \Ngo as you guys planned?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.46,0:05:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that pirates were
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.18,0:05:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,going to be easily encircled \Ninside the bay when we came out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they're scattered all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:06:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The broad-axe guy is yelling something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see what the Navy is up to!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.94,0:06:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, they leaked the information\N that they moved Ace's execution
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to make us rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then they slowly backed up
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.26,0:06:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and lured all the pirates \Ninside the bay, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.34,0:06:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...blocked the bay head with the\N human weapons to close the trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Checkmate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why Whitebeard said that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.52,0:06:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we should sink the Navy \Nships around us first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He saw it coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't get trapped, thanks to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we couldn't trap them,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.84,0:06:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can go at them from \Nthe front and the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.55,0:07:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack the allied pirates \Nfirst as we planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.16,0:07:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get rid of the ones who \Nwander off of the enclosure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,0:07:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle, is it okay if some Navy ships\N get caught in the crossfire?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.44,0:07:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it to a minimum.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.94,0:07:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's going on but \Nyou can't beat us that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.73,0:08:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Pacifistas!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He blew them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.27,0:09:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're even willing to sacrifice their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be afraid, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's charge the plaza without stopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.83,0:09:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Backing down is not even an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get to Ace before they get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, get off of the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.21,0:09:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Counter the human weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.33,0:10:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.62,0:10:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All units, get off of the ice right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.00,0:10:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let the pirates reach the plaza!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fall back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.78,0:10:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.02,0:10:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect that I'd get to fight the \Nworld's greatest swordsman in this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How lucky I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the number one\N swordsman of the Whitebeards.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:11:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see the Flower Sword's swordsmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have a good look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.86,0:11:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rose Rondo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of flower should I make bloom next?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.61,0:11:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drive them in, Pacifistas!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.23,0:11:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you! Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:12:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.38,0:12:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they made of?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not human!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they unbreakable?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.35,0:12:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much you struggle,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we will keep the upper hand, Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.22,0:12:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When all videos have been cut, \Nactivate the encircling walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.38,0:12:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thereupon, we will execute Ace \Nand round up all our enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:13:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace's in danger! I gotta hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.28,0:13:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The admiral has come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.36,0:13:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's tough but we need to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came here knowing that powerful \Nenemies would stand in our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.88,0:13:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die, Dragon's son!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.11,0:14:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace's brother, are you out of energy already?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The commanders are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a tremendous help!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get blocked by just one guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.44,0:14:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.90,0:14:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy is backing down \Nso now is our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.18,0:14:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's break through at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's kinda tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.79,0:14:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10th division commander--Curiel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.55,0:15:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna come for me,  \NI'll just knock you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.39,0:15:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're dead if you stay inside the bay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.24,0:15:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace will die and you guys \Nwill be trapped and wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.31,0:15:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't care less about who's gonna win
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.79,0:15:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it'll nice to see Whitebeard to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let Pops and Ace die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.63,0:15:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we put this match on hold, Vista?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.05,0:15:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like it'd be good for both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.18,0:15:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're ordered to back down, Smoker-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:16:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.86,0:16:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.85,0:16:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Hurry up and save your brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you cut the videos yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, give us another minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.13,0:16:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you find it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! We're still looking for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:32.04,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,PLEASE WAIT A MOMENT
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.06,0:16:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all set!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.16,0:16:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaffer, move aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.13,0:16:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They cut all videos except for one but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.62,0:16:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to wait?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're good to go on camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.12,0:16:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go on the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:16:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5 seconds to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:17:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4, 3, 2, 1, action!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.98,0:17:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The picture's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.49,0:17:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.64,0:17:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody's talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here at Marineford.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.04,0:17:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There're dead bodies of pirates and the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.27,0:17:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A commentary?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's this?! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.06,0:17:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm?! The guy over there must be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.29,0:17:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he's...! Don't tell me that he's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.22,0:17:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been hiding his origin but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he was one of the legendary crew of \Nthe King of the Pirates--Gold Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.35,0:17:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.64,0:17:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The great pirate--Captain Buggy the Clown?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's who I am indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.48,0:18:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's top secret but I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.78,0:18:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the legendary pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.67,0:18:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Captain Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.58,0:18:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your nose is bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.81,0:18:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut! Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.73,0:18:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wipe it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.46,0:18:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying "cut the stupid video right away!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.42,0:18:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't move on like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm afraid that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...one of the Video Transponder Snails
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.11,0:18:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has been stolen by the\N prisoners from Impel Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.60,0:18:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.37,0:18:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.65,0:18:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.31,0:18:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, now it's take 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3, 2, 1 and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.42,0:18:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That guy right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was one of Roger's legendary crew and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the sworn brother of "Red-Haired" \Nof The Four Emperors!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.29,0:18:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The great pirate--Captain Buggy the Clown?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.38,0:19:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop them right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.89,0:19:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.65,0:19:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They found us! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just got cut by the \Nfamous "Hawk-Eye" Mihawk
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.48,0:19:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you don't seem like you got hurt at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talking about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The legendary!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.48,0:19:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blow all of them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.94,0:19:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us see the war!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to other videos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.08,0:19:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us see Ace who was about to be executed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.13,0:19:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us see the group of Bartholomew Kumas!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.15,0:19:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They keep driving us to the corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.82,0:19:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.65,0:20:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't go down until we save Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.42,0:20:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.35,0:20:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.22,0:20:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Squard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.76,0:20:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that you're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, barely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.19,0:20:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I was calling for you a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it at the bay head now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.55,0:20:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your allies were beaten badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.00,0:20:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it here because\N I found the way out luckily.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.11,0:20:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sengoku has no mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.37,0:20:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's using all the forces he has\N in order to defeat us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:21:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops, did you notice what the Navy was up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.56,0:21:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've known Sengoku for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.98,0:21:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.57,0:21:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better for us if they're \Ngonna attack us from the rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go forward, too!\N We gotta invade without stopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.58,0:21:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.44,0:21:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Squard? Why is he up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.57,0:21:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are 43 allied captains here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.07,0:21:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we are all in your debt beyond words!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.15,0:21:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We risk our lives for the Whitebeard Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.48,0:21:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.63,0:21:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.39,0:21:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are fighting to save\N a member of your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.69,0:22:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pirate, Whitebeard,  \Nwon't give up on his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.09,0:22:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody followed you to this hell \Nbecause you're that kind of person.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.11,0:22:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.53,0:22:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we were also...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.93,0:22:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...members of your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.41,0:23:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one expected Squard's betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.63,0:23:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As they see him approaching Whitebeard,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.09,0:23:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,suspicion grows in the Navy men as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.19,0:23:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The strong bond shared among the \NWhitebeard Pirates has been destroyed...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.86,0:23:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the scenario described by the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.30,0:23:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.81,0:23:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Akainu's Plot! \NWhitebeard Entrapped!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.07,0:23:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
